    <tier id="COLLOQ_ROG-dialog-0029" speaker="ROG-dialog-0029" category="colloq" type="a" display-name="ROG-dialog-0029 [colloq]">
      <event start="T1-359" end="T6-929">Rada bi p@vedela, kaku je blo enkr@t, k@ smo odraščali v mladosti. </event>
      <event start="T6-929" end="T10-568">Jes sen se rodila v kmečki družini. </event>
      <event start="T10-568" end="T2">Kje s(), k(), ka() kaku je blo pr vs? </event>
      <event start="T2" end="T14-586">Tudi ste bli kmjeti doma? </event>
      <event start="T15-238" end="T8">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T8" end="T9">kmetje ste bli, </event>
      <event start="T9" end="T4">ne? </event>
      <event start="T4" end="T10">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T10" end="T19-117">Jes, </event>
      <event start="T19-117" end="T11">no, </event>
      <event start="T11" end="T12">jes sem mela pa samo eno sestro. </event>
      <event start="T12" end="T22-104">Ti si jih jemu? </event>
      <event start="T22-104" end="T23-340">Kolko? </event>
      <event start="T23-340" end="T17">Deset, </event>
      <event start="T17" end="T13">deset jih je blo, </event>
      <event start="T13" end="T25-378">ja. </event>
      <event start="T25-378" end="T14">Eee ... </event>
      <event start="T14" end="T15">kaku je blo, k si se ruodu? </event>
      <event start="T15" end="T16">Kje ste spali? </event>
      <event start="T16" end="T31-136">Ka ste jeli? </event>
      <event start="T31-136" end="T18">Jes, ti povem jes, ka san imela. </event>
      <event start="T18" end="T19">Jes sem mela štromac, </event>
      <event start="T19" end="T20">nut@r je mama dala une pjere @d f@rmentona, </event>
      <event start="T20" end="T381">u@n kantuon, </event>
      <event start="T381" end="T40-955">v sobi uoni smo spali. </event>
      <event start="T44-246" end="T45-983">Ja, ja. </event>
      <event start="T48-931" end="T23">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T23" end="T24">v k@štinah od ramarona smo spali, </event>
      <event start="T24" end="T25">vidiš. </event>
      <event start="T25" end="T51-984">Anka ... </event>
      <event start="T51-984" end="T55-607">ben jes je() eee jes sem spala n@ pjeri @d f@rmentuona. </event>
      <event start="T55-607" end="T55-936">Vidiš. </event>
      <event start="T56-726" end="T57-191">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T57-191" end="T382">Pole, več k@sno, ki smo zrasli, nnn sn eee smo imeli eno postelo od mojega nonota, </event>
      <event start="T382" end="T26">k je umru, </event>
      <event start="T26" end="T27">in smo spal jes in moja sestra na obej, obej na isti postelji. </event>
      <event start="T27" end="T68-258">Ena huor, ena duol. </event>
      <event start="T69-051" end="T69-399">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T69-399" end="T72-358">tu, tu, pr vas ne znam, kako je blo, ki vas je blo desjet. </event>
      <event start="T74-210" end="T75-462">Ja, ja. </event>
      <event start="T78-532" end="T78-930">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T78-930" end="T30">Vse sk@p v eni sobi. </event>
      <event start="T30" end="T31">No, ben, </event>
      <event start="T31" end="T32">mi smo imeli dve sobi, </event>
      <event start="T32" end="T85-891">je blo posebej eee mama in papa in posebe nona, nona. </event>
      <event start="T85-891" end="T33">Z nono smo spali mi. </event>
      <event start="T33" end="T34">Ja ja. </event>
      <event start="T34" end="T90-573">Ja, mi n@smo meli ... </event>
      <event start="T90-573" end="T36">kje, </event>
      <event start="T36" end="T35">kopalnic tabat ni blo, </event>
      <event start="T35" end="T37">ni blo stranišča v šiši, </event>
      <event start="T37" end="T38">nč ni blo, </event>
      <event start="T38" end="T94-970">ne. </event>
      <event start="T94-970" end="T39">Smo imeli na dvorišči mi ano, ano tašnu lesjenu baraku, </event>
      <event start="T39" end="T100-945">papa je naredu eno d@sko gor eee, </event>
      <event start="T100-945" end="T102-908">je eee eee na št() ... </event>
      <event start="T102-908" end="T41">Ma ne ne, </event>
      <event start="T41" end="T42">ni blo štrbunk. </event>
      <event start="T42" end="T107-798">Je prov eee malo višje, da si se vsel. </event>
      <event start="T107-798" end="T43">In eee je šlo, kamor je šlo, </event>
      <event start="T43" end="T113-076">t@m [zvok] u u u potak je šlo. </event>
      <event start="T113-076" end="T44">Pr vs eee tr@ba je blo isto, </event>
      <event start="T44" end="T115-831">ne? </event>
      <event start="T124-318" end="T48">Kandot, </event>
      <event start="T48" end="T126-123">ja. </event>
      <event start="T126-123" end="T49">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T49" end="T50">Ka ste se umivali vsaki dan? </event>
