      <event start="T323" end="T1000-152">Smo meli petnajst, št@rnajst let, petnajst. </event>
      <event start="T1000-152" end="T324">Ma nismo bivali gor, </event>
      <event start="T324" end="T1002-827">smo bivai v Izoli. </event>
      <event start="T1002-827" end="T325">Ma gor smo meli njive še tabot </event>
      <event start="T325" end="T326">in jes in Dario ... smo šli gor, </event>
      <event start="T326" end="T327">nekej so delali oni, </event>
      <event start="T327" end="T329">nekej š@pcali, </event>
      <event start="T329" end="T427">ka znam, </event>
      <event start="T427" end="T1011-228">ko ene trte, to. </event>
      <event start="T1011-228" end="T328">Woča ni blu. </event>
      <event start="T328" end="T331">Ma, </event>
      <event start="T331" end="T330">in pol nas je blu. </event>
      <event start="T330" end="T332">Pa sem reku: </event>
      <event start="T332" end="T333">"Mi gremo sami." </event>
      <event start="T333" end="T334">Seveda hod@t, </event>
      <event start="T334" end="T335">ne, </event>
      <event start="T335" end="T336">kaj, </event>
      <event start="T336" end="T1017-605">gor, z Izole gor. </event>
      <event start="T1017-605" end="T1019-129">Hodit. </event>
      <event start="T1019-129" end="T1020-090">In pole smo šli gor, </event>
      <event start="T1020-090" end="T337">uoni so pršli zraven. </event>
      <event start="T337" end="T1025-940">Je bil en mož tam, ki je koso ... koso travo v njivi. </event>
      <event start="T1025-940" end="T338">Je bil eee zid taku, </event>
      <event start="T338" end="T339">mi nismo bli visok, </event>
      <event start="T339" end="T1029-384">smo pogleal skuzi zid. </event>
      <event start="T1029-384" end="T1032-359">Inu smo vidli aaa angurije in melone. </event>
      <event start="T1032-359" end="T1034-291">Inu ponjer je, </event>
      <event start="T1034-291" end="T1038-437">uondi zgoraj je j@mu hišo, ki je, ki je, njegova žena. </event>
      <event start="T1038-437" end="T1041-808">Lih ta lih ta žena hodila v Trst, ki je vozila rubo to. </event>
      <event start="T1041-808" end="T1044-655">In on se je klicu Čir, Čir, ta muž. </event>
      <event start="T1044-655" end="T1048-532">"Čir, hodi damu, ki je kosilo." </event>
      <event start="T1048-532" end="T340">"Ja, </event>
      <event start="T340" end="T1050-517">pridem, vele, vele." </event>
      <event start="T1050-517" end="T341">[smeh] Je šu domu. </event>
      <event start="T341" end="T342">Mi smo š() [smeh] šli gor, </event>
      <event start="T342" end="T343">je j@mu žakelj, ki je verjetno mislu uon pobr@t melone in tu, </event>
      <event start="T343" end="T1058-588">smo obral mi. </event>
      <event start="T1058-588" end="T1061-220">[smeh] In je dol v staro hišo domu. </event>
      <event start="T1062-282" end="T1067-069">Ma in še z() in ponj je še zmerej je blo ta, ku da bi bla afera. </event>
      <event start="T1067-069" end="T428">Ma da na k@do je bil, </event>
      <event start="T428" end="T429">da kateri so bli, </event>
      <event start="T429" end="T430">da jes nisem vidu, </event>
      <event start="T430" end="T1071-706">da tu. </event>
      <event start="T1071-706" end="T344">In tu, ki je gledu. </event>
      <event start="T344" end="T345">Ka on zna, ku smo kopali uno prej, </event>
      <event start="T345" end="T346">ku smo kopali drug dan, </event>
      <event start="T346" end="T1075-431">n@č. </event>
      <event start="T1075-431" end="T1078-609">D@ so bli eni t@, da on ne zna, kašno podobnu. </event>
      <event start="T1078-609" end="T347">In pol da spet šu v: </event>
      <event start="T347" end="T349">"Ivan, </event>
      <event start="T349" end="T348">ma ka so bli toji otroci ta in ta dan te, te." </event>
      <event start="T348" end="T1084-771">"Ma da jes znam ne, da ..." </event>
      <event start="T1084-771" end="T1085-881">[glas] </event>
      <event start="T1085-881" end="T350">Mi smo samo mučali, ki ne smeš povedat n@č. [glas] </event>
      <event start="T350" end="T351">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T351" end="T352">to je taku, </event>
      <event start="T352" end="T353">take stvari so ble, </event>
      <event start="T353" end="T1090-360">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1090-360" end="T1092-853">Inu polej pa smo hodil pobirat češnje. </event>
      <event start="T1092-853" end="T354">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T354" end="T355">ma je tu. </event>
      <event start="T355" end="T356">Ma dama nisi smel jest, </event>
      <event start="T356" end="T1096-732">pobirat je blo za prodat. </event>
      <event start="T1096-732" end="T357">Alora, </event>
      <event start="T357" end="T1098-725">mi smo šli nabrat ... </event>
      <event start="T1100-578" end="T1101-858">Mi smo šli do enga druzga. </event>
      <event start="T1101-858" end="T1103-970">Jest, do ene druge. </event>
      <event start="T1103-970" end="T358">In uonde je bla ena češnja zraven hiše, </event>
      <event start="T358" end="T1107-264">malo več tan deleč. </event>
      <event start="T1107-264" end="T1112-723">A ena hiša je so bli te ljudje, ki smo jim rekli Pr Ravi, Otavijo, una, una. </event>
      <event start="T1112-723" end="T359">So bli gor. </event>
      <event start="T359" end="T431">Uni so bli gor, </event>
      <event start="T431" end="T1116-128">z gor se je vidlu lepo dol to češnjo. </event>
      <event start="T1116-128" end="T1118-093">Una je bla tude bolj zgodnja češnja. </event>
      <event start="T1118-093" end="T360">[glas] Sm reku zdej: </event>
      <event start="T360" end="T361">"Kaku mi gremo na to češnjo? </event>
      <event start="T361" end="T362">Ki je gor, </event>
      <event start="T362" end="T363">glej ga rod, </event>
      <event start="T363" end="T1122-985">nonštop." </event>
      <event start="T1122-985" end="T364">Dol, </event>
      <event start="T364" end="T1128-041">niso zdej ... s korte proč samo gledali to češnjo. </event>
      <event start="T1128-041" end="T432">In na žleb </event>
      <event start="T432" end="T365">inu pole smo šli, </event>
      <event start="T365" end="T1131-553">kaj smo zeli, en drat. </event>
      <event start="T1131-553" end="T366">En drat. </event>
      <event start="T366" end="T367">In smo se vseli, ki je bla taku korona, </event>
      <event start="T367" end="T368">češnja je bla nad korono. </event>
      <event start="T368" end="T1137-771">Smo vzel en drat. </event>
      <event start="T1137-771" end="T369">[nerazumljivo] Povlekli vejo dol </event>
      <event start="T369" end="T1143-014">inu inu inu jeli. [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1143-014" end="T370">Ma smo čuli gor, ki je s() krčala, ta njihova mat: </event>
      <event start="T370" end="T433">"Čuj, čuj, </event>
      <event start="T433" end="T434">Otavijo, Otavijo, </event>
      <event start="T434" end="T1148-536">hoj les. </event>
      <event start="T1148-536" end="T371">Dol p(), dol na češnji neki se juga." </event>
      <event start="T371" end="T1151-705">"Ma kaj ne viš, da piha burja?" </event>
      <event start="T1151-705" end="T1152-878">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1152-878" end="T1154-610">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1159-179" end="T377">Jes se ga, jes se ne spunem, </event>
      <event start="T377" end="T1162-203">jes se spunem zmerem ne eee ... </event>
      <event start="T1162-203" end="T1164-870">eee ne žejen, ne lačen. </event>
      <event start="T1164-870" end="T379">Vesel. </event>
      <event start="T379" end="T435">Evo </event>
      <event start="T435" end="T380">veselje je blo tabot, </event>
      <event start="T380" end="T1167-486">gotovo. </event>
      <event start="T1167-486" end="T1168-608">Mar si bil bos i nag. </event>
      <event start="T1168-608" end="T1170-198">Tabot. </event>
      <event start="T1171-478" end="T1172-092">Ja. </event>
