      <event start="T1032-359" end="T1034-291">Inu ponjer je, </event>
      <event start="T1034-291" end="T1038-437">ondi zgoraj je imel hišo, ki je, ki je, njegova žena. </event>
      <event start="T1038-437" end="T1041-808">Glih ta glih ta žena hodila v Trst, ki je vozila robo to. </event>
      <event start="T1041-808" end="T1044-655">In on se je klical Čir, Čir, ta mož. </event>
      <event start="T1044-655" end="T1048-532">"Čir, hodi domov, ki je kosilo." </event>
      <event start="T1048-532" end="T340">"Ja, </event>
      <event start="T340" end="T1050-517">pridem, vele, vele." </event>
      <event start="T1050-517" end="T341">[smeh] Je šel domov. </event>
      <event start="T341" end="T342">Mi smo š() [smeh] šli gor, </event>
      <event start="T342" end="T343">je imel žakelj, ki je verjetno mislil on pobrati melone in to, </event>
      <event start="T343" end="T1058-588">smo obrali mi. </event>
      <event start="T1058-588" end="T1061-220">[smeh] In je dol v staro hišo domov. </event>
      <event start="T1062-282" end="T1067-069">Ma in še z() in ponj je še zmeraj je bilo ta, ku da bi bila afera. </event>
      <event start="T1067-069" end="T428">Ma da na kdo je bil, </event>
      <event start="T428" end="T429">da kateri so bili, </event>
      <event start="T429" end="T430">da jaz nisem videl, </event>
      <event start="T430" end="T1071-706">da to. </event>
      <event start="T1071-706" end="T344">In to, ki je gledal. </event>
      <event start="T344" end="T345">Kaj on zna, ku smo kopali ono prej, </event>
      <event start="T345" end="T346">ku smo kopali drug dan, </event>
      <event start="T346" end="T1075-431">nič. </event>
      <event start="T1075-431" end="T1078-609">Da so bili eni to, da on ne zna, kakšno podobno. </event>
      <event start="T1078-609" end="T347">In pol da spet šel v: </event>
      <event start="T347" end="T349">"Ivan, </event>
      <event start="T349" end="T348">ma kaj so bili tvoji otroci ta in ta dan te, te." </event>
      <event start="T348" end="T1084-771">"Ma da jaz znam ne, da ..." </event>
      <event start="T1084-771" end="T1085-881">[glas] </event>
      <event start="T1085-881" end="T350">Mi smo samo molčali, ki ne smeš povedati nič. [glas] </event>
      <event start="T350" end="T351">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T351" end="T352">to je tako, </event>
      <event start="T352" end="T353">take stvari so bile, </event>
      <event start="T353" end="T1090-360">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1090-360" end="T1092-853">Inu pol pa smo hodili pobirat češnje. </event>
      <event start="T1092-853" end="T354">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T354" end="T355">ma je to. </event>
      <event start="T355" end="T356">Ma doma nisi smel jesti, </event>
      <event start="T356" end="T1096-732">pobirati je bilo za prodati. </event>
      <event start="T1096-732" end="T357">Alora, </event>
      <event start="T357" end="T1098-725">mi smo šli nabrat ... </event>
      <event start="T1100-578" end="T1101-858">Mi smo šli do enega drugega. </event>
      <event start="T1101-858" end="T1103-970">Jest, do ene druge. </event>
      <event start="T1103-970" end="T358">In onde je bila ena češnja zraven hiše, </event>
      <event start="T358" end="T1107-264">malo več tam daleč. </event>
      <event start="T1107-264" end="T1112-723">A ena hiša je so bili ti ljudje, ki smo jim rekli Pri Ravi, Ottavio, ona, ona. </event>
      <event start="T1112-723" end="T359">So bili gor. </event>
      <event start="T359" end="T431">Oni so bili gor, </event>
      <event start="T431" end="T1116-128">z gor se je videlo lepo dol to češnjo. </event>
      <event start="T1116-128" end="T1118-093">Ona je bila tudi bolj zgodnja češnja. </event>
      <event start="T1118-093" end="T360">[glas] Sem rekel zdaj: </event>
      <event start="T360" end="T361">"Kako mi gremo na to češnjo? </event>
      <event start="T361" end="T362">Ki je gor, </event>
      <event start="T362" end="T363">glej ga rod, </event>
      <event start="T363" end="T1122-985">nonstop." </event>
      <event start="T1122-985" end="T364">Dol, </event>
      <event start="T364" end="T1128-041">niso zdaj ... s korte proč samo gledali to češnjo. </event>
      <event start="T1128-041" end="T432">In na žleb </event>
      <event start="T432" end="T365">inu pol smo šli, </event>
      <event start="T365" end="T1131-553">kaj smo vzeli, en drat. </event>
      <event start="T1131-553" end="T366">En drat. </event>
      <event start="T366" end="T367">In smo se vsedli, ki je bila tako korona, </event>
      <event start="T367" end="T368">češnja je bila nad korono. </event>
      <event start="T368" end="T1137-771">Smo vzeli en drat. </event>
      <event start="T1137-771" end="T369">[nerazumljivo] Povlekli vejo dol </event>
      <event start="T369" end="T1143-014">inu inu inu jedli. [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1143-014" end="T370">Ma smo čuli gor, ki je s() kričala, ta njihova mat: </event>
      <event start="T370" end="T433">"Čuj, čuj, </event>
      <event start="T433" end="T434">Otavijo, Otavijo, </event>
      <event start="T434" end="T1148-536">hoj les. </event>
      <event start="T1148-536" end="T371">Dol p(), dol na češnji nekaj se juga." </event>
      <event start="T371" end="T1151-705">"Ma kaj ne vidiš, da piha burja?" </event>
      <event start="T1151-705" end="T1152-878">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1152-878" end="T1154-610">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1159-179" end="T377">Jaz se ga, jaz se ne spomnim, </event>
      <event start="T377" end="T1162-203">jaz se spomnim zmerom ne eee ... </event>
      <event start="T1162-203" end="T1164-870">eee ne žejen, ne lačen. </event>
      <event start="T1164-870" end="T379">Vesel. </event>
      <event start="T379" end="T435">Evo, </event>
      <event start="T435" end="T380">veselje je bilo tabot, </event>
      <event start="T380" end="T1167-486">gotovo. </event>
      <event start="T1167-486" end="T1168-608">Mar si bil bos in nag. </event>
      <event start="T1168-608" end="T1170-198">Tabot. </event>
      <event start="T1171-478" end="T1172-092">Ja. </event>
    </tier>
